    ---
    >> styles
      * = \\textit
      ** = \\textsf
      *** = \\texttt
    *italic*
    **sans-serif**
    ***teletype***
    ---
    \\textit{italic}
    \\textsf{sans-serif}
    \\texttt{teletype}
  '''

  testCase '''
    empty styles
    ---
    >>styles
    *italic*
    ---
    \\emph{italic}
  '''

